{"tid":570524,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"行超市秒秒攬腰護妻 ﻿梁詠琪﻿﻿有個暖男好老公","createTime":"2018-02-23T17:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T18:54:54.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"378c4c338239960bc549f0a6f4487314deb72717","tid":570524,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）呢排好忙，因為佢忙於四圍飛宣傳同城城主演嘅賀歲片《西遊記女兒國》，加上又要同鄭秀文拍新戲《八個女人一台戲》，過年前又要辦年貨，仲有湊女呢，所以一有時間佢就同老公Sergio 去超市入貨，來自西班牙嘅Sergio全程攬住老婆條腰，體貼度達100分。採訪︰李權威<br />\n<br />\n　　近期流感肆虐，過百所學校爆發流感，政府宣佈全港幼稚園、幼兒中心及小學提前放農曆新年假，家有一位讀學前班混血B女Sofia嘅GiGi，喺政府宣佈前一星期已醒目地同囡囡停學， 佢仲話會帶囡囡去空曠地方跑步做運動。<br />\n<br />\nGiGi好好笑容<br />\n<br />\n　　當日下晝4點，GiGi同老公及兩個女友人去ifc超市買嘢，女友人負責推購物車，Sergio負責扶住GiGi條腰，無論行定企，Sergio隻右手一定會緊貼老婆條腰，如果唔係GiGi 嚟緊要開Show，真係以為佢有咗。快買半個鐘，眾人離開，見GiGi搭自動電梯時同女友人傾得好開心，表現好雀躍，有個美滿家庭，事業又好，確實好值得開心嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/02/23/98460/wnep054p01a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F98460%2Fwnep054p01a.jpg&h=dead5dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/02/23/98460/wnep054p01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F98460%2Fwnep054p01b.jpg&h=50225a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/02/23/98460/wnep054p01c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F98460%2Fwnep054p01c.jpg&h=9c885aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/02/23/98460/wnep054p01d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F98460%2Fwnep054p01d.jpg&h=964d53b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.sth